## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6ebf5-103">O formulário estendido de um nome distinto inclui uma representação de cadeia de caracteres da propriedade objectGUID de um objeto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6ebf5-103">The extended form of a distinguished name includes a string representation of the objectGUID property of an object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6ebf5-104">Para objetos de entidade de segurança, como usuários, grupos e computadores, o formulário estendido também inclui uma representação de cadeia de caracteres da propriedade objectSID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6ebf5-104">For security principal objects such as users, groups, and computers, the extended form also includes a string representation of the objectSID property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6ebf5-105">Para obter mais informações sobre as propriedades de objectGUID e objectSID, consulte os tópicos [Object-Guid](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) e [Sid do objeto](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) na biblioteca MSDN, em [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6ebf5-105">For more information about the objectGUID and objectSID properties, see the topics [Object-Guid](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) and [Object-Sid](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6ebf5-106">O exemplo c# a seguir mostra como retornar uma coleção de nomes distintos em formato hexadecimal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6ebf5-106">The following C# example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```
